cast.name: 伊佩克·菲利兹·亚兹齐 Ipek Filiz Yazici

introduction: Are you ready to watch a love story full of adrenaline? Ese, a biker who wants to be the regional champion, and Deniz, who believes that she'll be taken away from the world by the UFOs one day, are two teenagers living totally different lives in Adana. With their youthful thrill, Deniz and Ese fall in love with one another. This great love brings two different worlds together. Ese will get prepared for the final race with the help of his love for Deniz, and she will discover her reality, thanks to the passion in his eyes. And nothing will be the same in their lives ever again. No matter the cost.
